<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email - {{appName}}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #333;">Welcome to {{appName}}!</h1>
    
    <p>Thank you for registering with {{appName}}. To complete your registration, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">
            Verify Email Address
        </a>
    </div>
    
    <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #666;">{{verificationUrl}}</p>
    
    <p>This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
    
    <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
        If you didn't create an account with {{appName}}, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>
</body>
</html>